Assets and Liabilities




Net Asset(Total asset - Total liability)




Negative
HK$0 to 1 mn
More than HK$1 mn to 3 mn
More than HK$3 mn to 5 mn
More than HK$5 mn to 10 mn
More than HK $10 mn





Saving Ratio(Saving amount / Monthly income)




0%
> 0% - 5%
> 5% - 10%
> 10% - 15%
> 15% - 20%
> 20%






